    "feat": {
        "name": "True Shapeshifter",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You transcend the limitations of form. Once per day you can cast *nature incarnate*, even if you don\u2019t have it prepared, to transform into a kaiju. If you have Plant Shape, you can choose to transform into a green man instead. You also gain the True Shapeshift activity.  \n  \n**True Shapeshift** (concentrate)",
        "level": 20,
        "traits": [
